        include issues with the thermostat, which can result in improper cooling, and condenser coil problems, which can lead
        to reduced efficiency. Thermostat repairs or replacements typically cost between $100 and $300, while condenser coil
        cleaning or replacement can range from $200 to $500. Regular maintenance, such as cleaning the coils and checking the
        thermostat, is essential to ensure these compact units operate efficiently.</p>
      <p><strong>Prep Table Coolers</strong></p>
